Documentation for Webserv :


1 - Try GET method :                For test a simple GET request, return the "get.html" file.

2 - Create file with POST :         For create and upload a file in the "upload" directory with a POST request.

3 - Upload file with POST :         For upload an existing file in the "upload" directory with a POST request.

4 - DELETE file :                   For delete a file in the "upload" directory with a DELETE request.

5 - See date and time :             Execute the cgi date.sh -> show server date and time.

6 - Go on youtube :                 Execute the cgi redirect.sh -> just a simple youtube redirection.

7 - Download help :                 Download this help (execute cgi download.py, POST).


